# Portent iOS

Bundle ID: `com.notitial.portent`. Swift 6, SwiftUI, MVVM, @Observable, URLSession. Targets iOS + macOS.

## Feature Structure

```
Features/<Name>/
  Data/       — Service impl, DTOs
  Domain/     — Service protocol, UseCase (optional)
  Presentation/ — ViewModel, View, State
```

## Mono Repo

Platform code lives here; shared docs in `portent/docs/`, `portent/core/`. See `docs/agents/agent-ios.md`.
